title: Street Center Lines (Deprecated August 2016)
description: OUTDATED. See the current data at https://data.cityofchicago.org/d/6imu-meau --Street center lines in Chicago. The data can be viewed on the Chicago Data Portal with a web browser. However, to view or use the files outside of a web browser, you will need to use compression software and special GIS software, such as ESRI ArcGIS (shapefile) or Google Earth (KML or KMZ), is required.
